  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants

    public class AaGui
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    Axioms and Analogies brute force axiom search. Class for GUI, main method, control flow No more hand-tinkering with code in the install phase: you only have to open your prover once using an ordinary "open file" dialog for the app to know where your prover is (and only once, not once per session).
    Author:
    Gordon Krieger
